name: Pyramid Sheesham Wood Incense Cone Box with Fretwork
description:
Pyramid Sheesham Wood Incense Cone Box with Fretwork
Our hand crafted range of Sheesham wood products are a must have range. Made from a hard Indian rosewood, each piece has either been carved with intricate fretwork designs or inlayed with metal details. Each has then been finished with a wax to protect and enhance the natural wood.
